title: Brady, Patriots take advantage of botched punt to beat Indy (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,361 Brady, Patriots take advantage of botched punt to beat Indy (Yahoo Sports) INDIANAPOLIS (AP) -- Tom Brady threw for 312 yards and three touchdowns and New England took advantage of a botched fake punt in the Patriots' 34-27 victory over the Indianapolis Colts on Sunday night.
